QuestData.Title: The Spirit and Body of Shen-zin Su
QuestData.Description: Well, that wraps it up here, doesn't it $n? Now that we've got these two roused and all friendly towards you, we just need to get them back to the Temple of Five Dawns.$B$BYou go ahead. I'm going to say my goodbyes, then I'll follow you up shortly.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring Shu and Wugou, the spirits of water and earth, to the Temple of Five Dawns. A cart is waiting near the road to take you there.
